SECTION 1. Any existing law to the contrary notwithstanding, salaries for the following positions in the Bureau of Public Works are hereby fixed as follows:

(a)Director, at eighteen thousand pesos

per annum;

(b)Assistant Director, at sixteen thousand eight hundred pesos

per annum;

(c)Chiefs of specialized technical or engineering divisions and regional supervisors, at

fifteen thousand six hundred pesos each

per annum;

and assistant chiefs of the above specialized divisions in the central office, and district engineers III, at fourteen thousand four hundred pesos each

per annum;

(d)Chiefs of other divisions in the central office, at twelve thousand pesos each

per annum;

(e)Chiefs of branches under the specialized technical or engineering divisions in the central office including district engineers II and flood control district engineers, at twelve thousand pesos each

per annum;

(f) Assistant chiefs of branches under the specialized technical divisions in the central office, assistant division chiefs of other divisions and district engineers and public works incharge in city engineering offices, at ten thousand two hundred pesos each

per annum.
